hosts.about:
A finance professional who loves traveling and is also a ski instructor. Grew up in Europe. Iv been fortunate to live in Spain, Andorra, born in Croatia, Italy, England and I was brought up in the greatest of places, Scotland :-)  

Style of travel is dependent on time leading up to trip for example it could be a 5 star relaxing holiday or an extreme sports holiday like skydiving or extrem skiing. 

My motto is respect. Respect my things, I respect yours.
